---
title: Dijon Pork Chops with Crispy Potato Cakes and Asparagus
description: A Dijon-shallot pan sauce takes these pork chops from delicious to company-worthy. Wringing out the potatoes is the secret to super crispy potato cakes. Don’t forget to season your potato cakes while they’re still hot!
